title: My Brother, My Brother and Me 222: The Rich Kids Camp
description:
It's a Max Fun Week special as we welcome John Hodgman to the program. He does an admirable, charitable job of pretending he knows who we are.

Suggested Talking Points: A Fate Worse than Public Defication, Papa John Refuses to Grow, A Day Without Doxxing, Bowser Went to Juliard.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
